events.name: ◆イベント　ティータ宅襲撃

parameters: 野盗がティータ宅に入っていくのを見てしまう。

Welcome to Hatayaki Village!... That's what it says. I
wonder what will happen to this village from now on.

Here are the fun pigs! Let's touch them with warmth and
become happy!

The crops have been destroyed... It's probably impossible to
use them as food anymore.

\SE[39]Eek... I didn't ask for this! \SE[28]There should
have been more time...!! ... ... ... \SE[58]By the way...

\SE[12]It's more... thorough than I thought.... \SE[38]It's
on a larger scale than expected, and I'm completely
surrounded. \SE[3]I completely miscalculated the
estimate.... I wonder if I can make it out of here alive
too....

\SE[0]Oh...! You're safe. You're quite the energetic older
sister. \!\SE[0]If you need anything, shall I supply you?

\SE[2]Will this place be my final resting place? \!\SE[0]I
must prepare myself for that possibility.

I am growing Prism Herb for pig farming. Stealing is a
crime. You should never do it. Don't you think it's pitiful
to see cute pigs go hungry?
